Our Network of Alliance Partners Deliver Results
and Maximize Client Technology Investments

IRVINE, CA – May 26th, 2021 — Neudesic, a business and technology consulting firm and leader in digital transformation, today announced it has been selected out of hundreds of global partners as the winner of the Databricks Innovation Partner Award for its inclusion of Databricks’ Lakehouse Architecture as the simple, open, and collaborative platform at the core of the Neudesic Data & AI Platform Accelerator. This accelerator, combined with industry expertise, has resulted in the development of multiple, repeatable solutions enabling migrations from legacy systems, real-time data transformations, and advanced analytics.
